			<h2 class="text-xl lg:text-2xl opacity-80 text-wrap max-w-[800px]"><span class="opacity-80">+2 years of experience in website creation and maintenance.</span><span class="text-yellow-200/90"> Web and Video Game Developer.</span> From the Canary Islands, Spain ðŸ‡ªðŸ‡¸. Specialized in creating applications and solutions.</h2>
